For non-inclusive private kindergartens that are also issued to teaching staff with a monthly basic living allowance of not less than 1660 yuan, Yinchuan City will arrange 6 months of subsidy funds as stable subsidy funds for early childhood teachers in accordance with the subsidy standard of 500 yuan per student per year.
