Chengdu people gather to watch the US Consulate, the police stop people from "looking too happy"
In response to the closure of the U.S. Consulate General in Houston, China announced the closure of the U.S. Consulate General in Chengdu on Friday.
On Saturday, the coat of arms of the U.S. Consulate was removed, and on Sunday, a dark glass car drove out of the consulate amid the boos of passers-by.
On Sunday, many Chengdu people gathered in front of the US Consulate to take pictures, and people who had not been came also came to take a look because of current affairs curiosity.
Agence France-Presse Chengdu station reporters also went to the Chengdu Consulate near the observation, sent back the news that the curious people are endless, and many parents take their children to take a walk to see the consulate, take pictures of the building, or take selfies.
The consulate was surrounded by guards, and from time to time the police were “righteous” people’s behavior, and they did not seem to allow any out-of-action behavior: a woman was stopped just as she was just beginning to prepare to sing a red song, and a guard confiscated a banner.
But residents of a nearby residential building managed to pull up a giant Chinese flag on their balconies and shout pro-China slogans.
The U.S. Consulate in Chengdu opened in 1985 and covers all U.S. consular affairs in southwestern China, especially in the Tibet Autonomous Region.
The Chinese government’s response to the U.S. is relatively restrained: many Chinese are online demanding that the government close the U.S. consulate in Hong Kong, but officials have only said that “the closure of the U.S. Consulate in Chengdu is a necessary and legitimate response to unreasonable U.S. actions by the United States.”
At present, in addition to Chengdu, the United States also has a presence in Guangdong, in Shanghai, in Shenyang, in Wuhan, and a consulate in Hong Kong.
Large-scale financial media action "walking the village live to see poverty alleviation" departure - Today's news - Hunan Daily Network - Huasheng Online
Hunan Daily · New Hunan client July 25th (Reporter of this newspaper) July 25th, by the Central Radio and Television General Financial Program Center sponsored by the large-scale financial media action "walking the village live to see poverty alleviation" from Xuzhou, Jiangsu Province, two caravans carrying 5G new media mobile cloud broadcasting system at the scene of the guests watching, slowly appeared.
General Secretary Xi Jinping pointed out that "2020 is a landmark year, we will build a well-off society in an all-round way, achieve the first century of struggle, and 2020 is also the year of decisive victory in the fight against poverty."
The large-scale financial media action "Going to the village to see poverty alleviation" is an important measure for the Central Radio and Television General Administration's financial program center to cooperate with this major theme and do a good job in poverty alleviation propaganda.
The action will enter more than 20 provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government poverty alleviation villages across the country, excavate the story of living poverty alleviation, directly attack the great changes in the appearance of the village, and show how the villagers can break through the difficulties of survival and development and move towards the road to wealth.
The operation will take more than three months.
The reporter started from Xuzhou, the soldiers were divided into two ways, all the way to the southwest line, passing through Anhui, Hubei, Jiangxi, Hunan, Guangxi, Guizhou, Sichuan, Chongqing, Yunnan, Tibet and other places; the other way to the northwest line, passing through Henan, Shaanxi, Gansu, Qinghai, Xinjiang, Ningxia, Inner Mongolia, Shanxi, Hebei and other places, the journey of more than 10,000 kilometers.
In the form of reporting, "walking the village live to see poverty alleviation" bold integration.
The economic development of the caravan to the village will be broadcast through the Central Radio and Television General Station CCTV Finance Channel, the Central Wide Economic Voice, China Transport Broadcasting, and the CCTV New Financial Media.
Among them, the TV live broadcast will be mainly completed in the CCTV financial channel's noon news program "world finance" (first broadcast time: Monday to Sunday 12:00-13:00), CCTV financial channel's gold news column "economic information simulcast" will open a poverty alleviation report column (first broadcast time: Monday to Sunday 20:30-21:30).
At the same time, the caravan will be in each village in the CCTV financial client for up to 1 hour of live broadcast, the audience by downloading the CCTV financial APP, you can watch the live broadcast, participate in the raffle.
In the application of technology and studio design, "walking the village to see poverty alleviation" dared to break through, the first "outfield new media caravan".
The car is equipped with a 5G new media mobile cloud broadcasting system, using 5G+4K/8K+AI technology to achieve online and offline, large screen and small screen, and an organic combination of TV broadcasts.
Configure the three-sun broadcast area, the studio area is converted from a container, 12 meters long, 2.55 meters wide, 3.98 meters high, the box using hydraulic automatic expansion structure, the maximum can be turned 120 degrees.
The studio area can also be automatically expanded and externally expanded to an area of more than 50 square meters, which can meet the scene requirements of most programs.
